Authors:
    Thomas Moerwald, moerwald(at)acin.tuwien.ac.at
    Johann Prankl
    Michael Zillich
    Markus Vincze

Modules:
    - TomGine (OpenGL rendering, geometry)
    - TomGineIP (OpenGL image processing)
    - Tracker (OpenGL object tracking)
    - Recognizer3D (SIFT based object recognition)

Executables:
    - trackerQt (Qt interface for object tracking and recognition)

Requirements:
    Linux (Ubuntu,...)
	rt		(real-time clock)
	freeglut3-dev
    libglew1.6-dev
	libftgl2, libftgl-dev (render text in OpenGL)
	OpenCV    

Installation:
    cd ${INSTALL_DIR}/3.0
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ..
    make
    sudo make install

Execution:
    cd ${INSTALL_DIR}/3.0/bin
    ./trackerQt

Troubleshooting:
    mail: moerwald(at)acin.tuwien.ac.at

